text = "[font_size=34][b]ACHIEVEMENTS[/b][/font_size]

[b]First Compile[/b] - Build the prototype.
[b]Full Deck[/b] - Make a 32-card deck.
[b]Street Clear[/b] - Beat the Street Enforcer.
[b]Bit Storm[/b] - Reach 150+ bits in combat.

More achievements can be wired to save data later."

