text = "[font_size=34][b]INFORMATION[/b][/font_size]

GDC DEMO is a rough neon-sketch card-combat prototype.

Build a 32-card deck, spend bits to play cards, and survive encounter rounds. The UI is intentionally built from editable Godot scene nodes so it can be moved and tuned in the editor."

